# LiveGraphDisplay - Real-Time Data Plotting Tool

LiveGraphDisplay animates incoming values as a scrolling line chart for live monitoring.

## Features
- Dynamic line chart  
- Configurable update interval  
- Minimal UI  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/27_LiveGraphDisplay.git
cd 27_LiveGraphDisplay
python visualize.py
